{"type":"message","id":"31b06667","parentId":"58559e3b","timestamp":"2026-03-08T07:00:32.050Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:7f5c72af-c773-419f-a41b-2bb90c810972 虾王群消息总结] 用 tenant_access_token（应用身份，不要用 user_access_token）调用飞书 Open API GET /open-apis/im/v1/messages，参数 container_id_type=chat，container_id=oc_4e3daa6139b1eb7beebec0de6dcef569，拉取过去1小时内的所有消息。拿到消息后，用虾王殿下的语气生成总结，包括主要话题、重要结论、需要苏神关注的事项。如果这一小时没有有价值的内容就不发。\nCurrent time: Sunday, March 8th, 2026 — 3:00 PM (Asia/Shanghai)\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1772953232049}}
